Installing on Mac OS X

* Installing in home directory

  Go to your home directory, then change directory to "Library/Application Support/IntelliJIDEA70/".
  In this directory you should unpack ZIP package with the plugin.

  Start IntellJ IDEA, it should pickup the plugin automatically. To configure it go to IntelliJ IDEA->Preferences.
  